Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.49,0:27:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通布里斯托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not exactly the ammo of choice
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.34,0:27:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小混混们会选择的弹药  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of your average Bristol low-life, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.38,0:27:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他们刚认出了他  如果你感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think they've just identified him, if you're interested.
