Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.18,0:28:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么会出现在你的调查里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How have they popped up on your radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟我们盯着的毒贩打了交道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're playing footsie with a drug gang in our patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.58,0:28:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就有问题了  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you have got a problem, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.82,0:28:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.62,0:28:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你找上他们  八成是要挑起战争  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those are the guys you call if you want to start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.66,0:29:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.08,0:29:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong?
