Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.90,0:29:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我已经报警了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I've already called the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们死者是斯特凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}told them it was Stefan.
