Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.54,0:29:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧昂卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bianca?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.11,0:29:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧昂卡  那些桌子不会自己变干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bianca, those tables won't lay themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.83,0:29:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You ok?
