Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.47,0:30:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道我们不该把他埋在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew we shouldn't have buried him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.11,0:30:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what shall we do?
