Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.39,0:30:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有道理  他们需要武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that makes sense. They'll need fire power.
