Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.06,0:31:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  他们会联系到米密查家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God, they'll make the connection to the Mimicas
